ext story\n252\t```\n253\t\n254\t## Command UX: `codeharness init`\n255\t\n256\t### Successful Init\n257\t\n258\t```\n259\t$ codeharness init\n260\t\n261\t── Stack Detection ────────────────────────────────────────────\n262\t[OK] Stack: Node.js (package.json)\n263\t[OK] App type: CLI\n264\t\n265\t── Dependencies ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n266\t[OK] Docker: running\n267\t[OK] Showboat: installed (v0.6.1)\n268\t[OK] agent-browser: installed (v1.2.0)\n269\t[OK] OTLP: Node.js packages installed\n270\t\n271\t── Observability ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n272\t[OK] Shared stack: already running at ~/.codeharness/stack/\n273\t     └ VictoriaLogs :9428  VictoriaMetrics :8428  OTel :4318\n274\t\n275\t── BMAD ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n276\t[OK] BMAD: installed (v6.2.0)\n277\t[OK] Patches: 5 applied (story, dev, review, retro, sprint)\n278\t\n279\t── Project Setup ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n280\t[OK] State: .claude/codeharness.local.md created\n281\t[OK] Docs: AGENTS.md + docs/ scaffold created\n282\t[OK] Enforcement: front:OFF db:OFF api:OFF obs:ON\n283\t\n284\tReady. Run: codeharness run\n285\t```\n286\t\n287\t### Init with OpenSearch\n288\t\n289\t```\n290\t$ codeharness init --opensearch-url https://search.example.com\n291\t\n292\t── Observability ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n293\t[OK] OpenSearch: connected (https://search.example.com)\n294\t     └ Logs: ✓  Metrics: ✓  Traces: ✓\n295\t[INFO] No local Docker stack needed — using remote OpenSearch\n296\t```\n297\t\n298\t### Init Failure (Actionable)\n299\t\n300\t```\n301\t$ codeharness init\n302\t\n303\t── Dependencies ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n304\t[OK] Docker: running\n305\t[FAIL] Showboat: not found\n306\t       → Install: pip install showboat\n307\t       → Or: uv tool install showboat\n308\t[OK] OTLP: Node.js packages installed\n309\t\n310\t── Observability ────────────────────────────────