{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01ELiUhcroCmkW9Cb6Be3ouH","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\nImplementation complete. Here is what was done:\n\n**Task 1 — `codeharness run` wired to workflow engine:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/commands/run.ts` — replaced the \"temporarily unavailable\" placeholder with real workflow engine calls: `parseWorkflow()` -> `resolveAgent()` + `compileSubagentDefinition()` -> `executeWorkflow()`. Added `--resume` flag. Added early exit when no stories are ready (AC #9). Maps `--max-iterations` to `EngineConfig.maxIterations`.\n\n**Task 2 — `codeharness status` shows workflow state:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/status/formatters.ts` — added `readWorkflowState` import, `formatElapsed()` helper, `printWorkflowState()` for human display, `getWorkflowStateData()` for JSON output. Shows phase, iteration, tasks completed, elapsed time (only when executing), evaluator scores, and circuit breaker state. Missing state file shows \"No active workflow run\".\n\n**Task 3 — Unit tests:**\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/commands/__tests__/run.test.ts` — rewrote with mocks for `parseWorkflow`, `resolveAgent`, `compileSubagentDefinition`, `executeWorkflow`. Tests: config construction, success/failure paths, no-stories-ready exit, workflow parse failure, agent resolution failure.\n- `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/modules/status/__tests__/formatters-workflow.test.ts` — new file with tests for: no active run, executing state display, circuit breaker triggered, elapsed time omitted for non-executing, JSON output shape, formatElapsed edge cases.\n\n**Results:** 4036 tests pass, 156 test files, zero regressions. Clean TypeScript compilation. Story marked `review`.\n\n## Session Issues\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 24\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 10, Edit: 7, Grep: 2, Write: 2, Glob: 1\n- Largest Bash